# Defensive — MagicMock/ leaks from broken test fixtures coercing a
# mocked workspace root into a real Path. The 2026-05-17 incident
# wrote real files into "MagicMock/mock.root/<id>/...". The
# bizniz/lib/path_guard.py now blocks this in production; this
# .gitignore entry keeps any future regression silent in git.
MagicMock/
